WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.316
Interview at Swiss Hotel, Istanbul (Turkey)
24 April 2001

00:01.341 --> 00:06.388
Interpreter: How do you reach to
all the human beings all over the world?

00:06.521 --> 00:09.770
See, there are so many people in this world,

00:09.795 --> 00:14.285
in these modern times,
are seeking the truth.

00:26.598 --> 00:30.167
So, there are so many false people
also in this world

00:30.192 --> 00:32.731
who wants to make money out of them.

00:52.863 --> 00:57.940
Interpreter:Why the people prefers your way

00:57.988 --> 01:01.276
because of Your innocence and the Purity.

01:01.355 --> 01:04.588
Yes, you have to have the truth, you see.

01:04.612 --> 01:08.916
So they discard what is not the truth
and come to me.

01:25.898 --> 01:30.076
Interpreter: How is Turkish people for realisation?

01:30.101 --> 01:34.270
You are coming to Turkey since last 10 years.

01:34.295 --> 01:38.409
Wonderful people.
They are one of the best I have seen.

01:48.875 --> 01:52.368
When you compare with
other countries in the world,

01:52.393 --> 01:54.945
how do you find Turkish people?

01:54.970 --> 01:56.793
Very good. Excellent.

01:56.843 --> 01:59.843
They are very simple people and innocent.

01:59.868 --> 02:03.068
They don’t accept nonsense much.

02:25.496 --> 02:29.060
Interpreter:  There is an economic crisis
at this moment in Turkey.

02:29.085 --> 02:33.045
Can we overcome this crisis and
how can we overcome this crisis?

02:33.070 --> 02:35.992
By the grace of God, everything
can be work out.

02:36.032 --> 02:39.338
There are so many realized souls
in this country

02:39.363 --> 02:41.930
that they will be helped very much.

02:42.041 --> 02:48.779
It is most important thing that you have
to become very peaceful, joyous and happy.

03:10.988 --> 03:16.842
Interpreter: Minister who is responsible
from the finance of Turkey,

03:16.900 --> 03:18.790
How do you see him?

03:20.602 --> 03:23.288
Kemal Dervish, his name is Kemal Dervish.

03:23.313 --> 03:26.084
Yes yes, I have seen his photograph.

03:26.116 --> 03:28.586
He is nice man but very hard working.

03:28.611 --> 03:32.618
So, I think he should take little easy.

03:44.022 --> 03:49.854
Because you see, these hard works
can make your heart weak.

03:49.862 --> 03:54.002
So, He is very precious man,
he should look after him.

04:15.678 --> 04:19.003
Interpreter:Tonight..the..
you have a big seminar.

04:19.028 --> 04:23.333
What will happen to the people
who comes there?

04:23.358 --> 04:26.629
I think they will all get their self realizations.

04:36.465 --> 04:39.469
Interpreter:Can I have my self realization?
She is asking.,

04:39.494 --> 04:41.037
Of course, of course.

04:50.492 --> 04:51.523
It’s a most important thing.

04:51.555 --> 04:54.182
You don’t have to pay for it.
You don’t have to do anything.

04:54.207 --> 04:58.475
But you must respect yourself and
go deep down into yourself to know

04:58.483 --> 05:00.470
what are your values.

05:06.137 --> 05:07.684
It is miraculous.

05:11.579 --> 05:13.019
May God bless you.

05:17.936 --> 05:19.331
What is it?

05:24.264 --> 05:27.181
Interpreter: She says,
“She is feels positive energy,

05:27.206 --> 05:29.722
love  from you while talking”.

05:29.747 --> 05:32.096
That’s the way thing.
We have to Love.

05:32.144 --> 05:34.177
Love is the main force

05:34.202 --> 05:37.915
which has created this world
which has created us,  we have forgot...
